<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ج ز ف:</span> <span class="c2">(الْجَزْفُ)</span> بِوَزْنِ الضَّرْبِ أَخْذُ الشَّيْءِ <span class="c2">(مُجَازَفَةً)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(جِزَافًا)</span> فَارِسِيٌّ مُعَرَّبٌ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>